Silicon Labs Gecko HAL
######################

Origin:
   Silicon Labs Gecko SDK
   https://www.silabs.com/products/development-tools/software/simplicity-studio

Version:
   v2.7.3

Purpose:
   Add support for Silicon Labs EXX32 SoCs

Description:
   This code component is used to add Zephyr support for Silicon Labs EXX32 SoCs.
   To speed up the development process it is based on the Silicon Labs HAL.

   The Silicon Labs HAL is split into SoC specific folders. They share the 
   Peripheral Support library.

   The following folders are imported:
   platform/Device/SiliconLabs/$(GECKO_DEVICE)
   platform/emlib

Dependencies:
   This source code depends on headers and sources from Zephyr:
   ext/hal/cmsis

URL:
   https://www.silabs.com/products/development-tools/software/simplicity-studio

Maintained-by:
   External

License:
   Apache 2.0 and proprietary

How to update
+++++++++++++

  * git clone https://github.com/SiliconLabs/wfx-fullMAC-driver.git
  * cd wfx-fullMAC-driver
  * git archive master | (cd /path/to/hal_silabs/wfx/; tar xvvf -)
  * cd ..
  * git clone https://github.com/SiliconLabs/wfx-fullMAC-tools.git
  * cd wfx-fullMAC-tools
  * git archive master:Examples/SiliconLabs/shared sdio | (cd /path/to/hal_silabs/wfx/; tar xvvf -)
  * Replace sdio IRQ handling
